by xabbuh at 2019-07-31T12:00:30Z

I asked Oskar to open this PR as I agree with the reasoning for the changes. Dumping `null` by default is good, but being able to get `~` instead allows to keep files more similar to what we use in the documentation. While I generally agree with not adding more options than necessary the impact here is rather limited and doesn't add much complexity. So ðŸ‘ from me.

